info.description:
# podsay
This is a Python implementation (though not a faithful port) of [https://github.com/kevinschaul/yosay](https://github.com/kevinschaul/yosay).

# Installation
`pip install podsay`

# Usage

	from podsay.podsay import podsay
	podsay("Hello, world!")

# License
